++## Endpoints bridge (API)
++
++### Lecture
++```
++POST /clone/read
++Body: { type: "nfc" | "rfid125k" | "ir" | "subghz_433" | "subghz_868" | "barcode" | "ble_adv", timeout_ms?: 10000 }
++Response: {
++  ok: true,
++  format: "EM4102",
++  raw_hex: "...",
++  pronto: "...",   // pour IR
++  ndef: [...],     // pour NFC
++  id: "0xABCDEF12", // pour badges
++  rssi: -42,       // pour BLE
++  learned_at: ISO8601
++}
++```
++
